tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE patient_outcomes (
    patient_id INT,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50),
    admission_date DATE,
    discharge_date DATE,
    diagnosis VARCHAR(100),
    treatment VARCHAR(100),
    outcome VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(255),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  diagnosis VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE Outcomes (
  outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  outcome_date DATE,
  readmission BOOLEAN,
  outcome_description TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES Patients(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(50),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  admission_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE treatments (
  treatment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  treatment_name VARCHAR(50),
  treatment_date DATE,
  cost DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE Treatments (
  treatment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  treatment_name VARCHAR(50),
  treatment_date DATE,
  cost DECIMAL(10, 2),
  FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES Patients(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Diagnoses (
  diagnosis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  diagnosis_name VARCHAR(50),
  diagnosis_date DATE,
  description TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES Patients(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50),
    patient_age INT,
    admit_date DATE,
    discharge_date DATE,
    diagnosis VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE admissions (
    admission_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    admit_date DATE,
    discharge_date DATE,
    diagnosis VARCHAR(100),
    treatment_plan TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE treatments (
    treatment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    treatment_name VARCHAR(50),
    cost DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE outcomes (
    outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    admission_id INT,
    discharge_date DATE,
    outcome_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE quality_indicators (
    indicator_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    indicator_name VARCHAR(50),
    indicator_score INT,
    benchmark_score INT
)
